  "title": "supervisor",
  "description": "<h1><strong>Recruitment — Cleaning Supervisor (Singapore)</strong></h1><p>We are looking for a <strong>Cleaning Supervisor</strong> to join our operations team.</p><h2><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Assign and supervise daily cleaning tasks</p></li><li><p>Manage roster and deployment of cleaners</p></li><li><p>Communicate with clients on site requirements & feedback</p></li><li><p>Monitor cleaning standards and safety procedures</p></li><li><p>Handle basic inventory of cleaning supplies and equipment</p></li><li><p>Assist in training new staff on work processes</p></li><li><p>Respond to on-site issues and report updates to management</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Supervisory / team leader experience preferred (cleaning industry is a plus)</p></li><li><p>Able to coordinate manpower and scheduling</p></li><li><p>Basic communication ability (English / Mandarin or simple communication)</p></li><li><p>Responsible, hardworking, and reliable</p></li><li><p>Able to work in mall/office/building/industrial site environments</p></li><li><p>Singapore work experience preferred</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Employment Details:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Salary: <strong>Negotiable / Based on experience</strong></p></li><li><p>Working Hours: <strong>Roster / Day or Night shift (based on project)</strong></p></li><li><p>Location: <strong>Islandwide projects</strong> (deployment depends on site)</p></li><li><p>Benefits: <strong>Annual leave, Public holiday, OT compensation</strong> (subject to company policy)</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Suitable For:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Cleaning supervisors / team leaders / on-site ICs</p></li><li><p>Candidates seeking stable, long-term roles</p></li></ul>",
